      "text": "Madden NFL 2000 (also known as Madden 2000) is a football video game developed by EA Tiburon and published by EA Sports in 1999 for PlayStation, Nintendo 64, and Microsoft Windows. A Mac OS port was published by Aspyr Media; it was the first football game ever ported to Mac.",
